adsController.clickhere: (Click Activate to enable your new Notch)
adsController.dialogfirstline: Please read these instructions to proceed

NextContent.textcontent: Dynamic Island Activates the IOS 16 Notch feature on your Android Phone
Various Styles & Themes which you can choose from Settings
Easy to activate and it has a very user-friendly interface
Built-In Battery Saver to offer you best quality with less battery usage
Smooth animations simulated from the iPhone 14 Pro
Expandable Notch bar to contain your notification in a Modern Interface
Control your outgoing calls from your Dynamic Island Notch
Incoming calls will make your Notch Expand and give you ability to respond
Works with most of the AirPods and other Wireless Earphones
Responsive to multi-screen size no matter how big or small is your Phone screen
Fully customizable options to give you the freedom to choose your Styles
Receive future updates for Free & for lifetime
You will see the Notch Bar on top of your screen immediately after granting the required access
Tapping on the Notch Bar will show you the available options
Suports the Audio Mixer (Equalizer) when Music is playing
